{"tid":2071803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支那或成最大贏家]北京再有22宗本土感染","createTime":"2020-06-20T06:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T09:49:55.000Z","uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ab0cab59af04115edc3c8731eb8576e87342115e","tid":2071803,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T06:18:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533117-20200620.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533117-20200620.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w3fp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=cd73b021\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533117-20200620.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=697188d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533117-20200620.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地過去一日新增27宗新型肺炎確診病例，23宗是本土感染，北京佔22宗，河北1宗。北京再多4宗疑似病例。全國累積83352人確診，4634人死亡，78000多人康復出院。<br />\n<br />\n北京自上星期四以來，有超過200宗確診病例，昨日新增的22宗病例，新發地市場所在的豐台區佔13宗，大興區8宗，當局在大興區近3千個農產品市場及餐飲食堂等全面消毒，為超過2萬人進行病毒檢測。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02551826eba71665fecbabb5ebfdf525eb5ac5b5","tid":2071803,"uid":5737,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T06:46:23.000Z","msg":"光復北京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京肺炎：香港人 睇好了 我只示範一次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4d42da9e0cc8e81b93a34